fields.name: Notes:
fields.value: Jahoda can be used to enable Ascendent Gleam in non-Nod-krai characters. She pairs best with Ineffa. However, she doesn't current have a team where she is the premier unit. She can be slotted into most teams as the Anemo unit with __Viridescent Venerer__ or other supportive sets.
